		(descr "WS2815, 6-pin PLCC6 5.0x5.0mm, 1.6mm pad pitch. Pad numbering corrected to match the real WS2815 pin diagram (VCC=1, VDD=2, DO=3, DIN=4, GND=5, BIN=6) - see https://www.normandled.com/upload/201808/WS2815%20LED%20Datasheet.pdf. NOT the same pin numbering as KiCad's stock LED_WS2812_PLCC6 footprint, which is for the different 6-pin WS2812 part (pin 1=DO, pin 4=NC).")
